{
  "message": "test(fuzz): add 28 signature_parsing corpus seeds\n\nCovers gufunc and fixed signature parsing patterns:\n- Basic signatures: scalar, reduce, elementwise\n- Common operations: dot, matmul, transpose\n- Multi-output: (m,n)->(m),(n)\n- Higher dimensions: 3D reduce, 4D passthrough\n- Broadcasting: (),(n)->(n)\n- N-ary inputs: ternary, quad, quint operations\n- Edge cases: empty, single scalar/dim, ellipsis\n- Optional dimensions: (?), (n,?)\n- Dimension naming: numeric (10), uppercase (N), alphanumeric (a1)\n- Einsum-style: (m,k),(k,n)->(m,n)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
